{"tid":789803,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急求助］隻龜吐血","createTime":"2018-08-22T13:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T03:18:22.000Z","uid":102358,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0695a92c7b4b73435f0524a449eb202c17dc0f66","tid":789803,"uid":102358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"每日會有一段時間放龜係浴缸俾佢爬下<br />\n頭先幫隻貓換貓砂 貓砂盤跌左落去壓到隻龜<br />\n佢即時吐左血 之後好虛弱郁唔到 一張開口都有血水<br />\n後尾吐哂啲血就無事 爬得走得 但係唔肯食野 同埋佢左眼開唔到...<br />\n有無巴絲有睇龜既診所介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手養龜無睇開獸醫 上網搵過話土瓜灣有間幾好 有無巴絲有睇過？<br />\n而家隻龜應該乾養定濕養好⋯同埋有無其他野食可以俾佢食住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/212741_eb89d8307710a7c7bb5788478e3d873a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F212741_eb89d8307710a7c7bb5788478e3d873a.png&h=8336a1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻龜養左兩個幾月仲係好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7330522385164ac09966165c27883563cc2c9f9e","tid":789803,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"去睇獸醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莫講child 登得班小朋友唔會有獸醫，就算有都好，你expect 點樣靠睇相知佢乜事呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee3a992b05c9488bf8be301e57b8efd1827dbd9","tid":789803,"uid":102358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7330522385164ac09966165c27883563cc2c9f9e","tid":789803,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"去睇獸醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莫講child 登得班小朋友唔會有獸醫，就算有都好，你expect 點樣靠睇相知佢乜事呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow